Start Mononoke
  $ start_and_wait_for_mononoke_server  
  $ lfs_uri="$(lfs_server)/repo"

Setup common client configuration for these tests
  $ cat >> "$HGRCPATH" <<EOF
  > [extensions]
  > amend=
  > infinitepush=
  > commitcloud=
  > remotenames=
